description:
Serge Normant takes us through his career, from the early days of shared rooms to his big time salon in New York. Plus, some inevitable conversation on where the industry is headed (and how many products you'll need for the journey). Before that: Jenn's first couple's massage; the new millennial fragrances; and you asked, we answered: Is dermaplaning screwing up your skin?
